@startuml
!theme plain
autonumber


actor "Logistics Operator" as Actor
participant "User Interface\n(Single Page App)" as UI
participant "Backend Service\n(Port System REST API)" as Backend

Actor -> UI : 1: manage qualifications
activate UI
UI -> Backend : 1.1: Request (POST/PUT/GET /api/qualifications)
activate Backend
Backend --> UI : 1.2: Response (QualificationDto / List<...>)
deactivate Backend
UI --> Actor : 1.3: Display qualification data / confirmation
deactivate UI

@enduml